---
import BaseLayout from "../components/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Victor de Alcântara Bueno — Projetos"
  description="Engenharia de software com foco em offline-first, integrações críticas e UX operacional. Cases, stack e contato direto."
>
  <Fragment slot="nav">
    <a class="c-nav-logo" href="/">Victor<span>®</span></a>
    <div class="c-nav-links">
      <a href="#projetos">Projetos</a>
      <a href="#sobre">Sobre</a>
      <a href="#contato">Contato</a>
    </div>
    <div class="c-nav-right">
      <div class="c-nav-lang">
        <a href="/client" class="active">PT</a>
        <span>/</span>
        <a href="/en/client">EN</a>
      </div>
      <a href="#contato" class="c-nav-cta">Falar sobre projeto</a>
    </div>
  </Fragment>

  <div class="page-client">
  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="c-hero">
    <p class="c-hero-eyebrow">Engenharia de Software · Disponível para projetos em 2026</p>
    <h1 class="c-hero-headline">
      Produtos que <em>funcionam</em><br />quando mais importa.
    </h1>
    <p class="c-hero-sub">
      Construo sistemas web e mobile com foco em confiabilidade operacional,
      integrações que não falham sob pressão e entrega previsível de ponta a ponta.
    </p>
    <a href="#contato" class="c-hero-action">
      Falar sobre seu projeto →
    </a>
  </section>

  <div class="c-section-divider"><hr /></div>

  <!-- PROJETOS -->
  <section class="c-projects" id="projetos">
    <p class="c-section-label">Projetos selecionados</p>

    <div class="c-projects-grid">

      <!-- Nexus -->
      <a class="c-project-card" href="/projects/p7/">
        <img
          class="c-project-img"
          src="/images/3f015622-01e5-46c9-a13c-c655373c819a.png"
          alt="Plataforma Nexus — check-in offline e painel administrativo"
          loading="lazy"
        />
        <div class="c-project-body">
          <div class="c-project-meta">
            <span class="c-project-year">2024</span>
            <span class="c-project-tag">Risco</span>
          </div>
          <h2 class="c-project-name">Plataforma Nexus</h2>
          <p class="c-project-desc">
            Ingressos, vendas via WhatsApp, pagamentos integrados e check-in offline-first na portaria de eventos.
          </p>
          <p class="c-project-kpi">✦ 100% check-in offline — operação sem rede</p>
          <span class="c-project-link">Ver case →</span>
        </div>
      </a>

      <!-- Habit Analyzer -->
      <a class="c-project-card" href="/projects/p3/">
        <img
          class="c-project-img"
          src="/images/analytics-code.svg"
          alt="Habit Analyzer — dashboard de analytics e código"
          loading="lazy"
        />
        <div class="c-project-body">
          <div class="c-project-meta">
            <span class="c-project-year">2023</span>
            <span class="c-project-tag">Custo</span>
          </div>
          <h2 class="c-project-name">Habit Analyzer</h2>
          <p class="c-project-desc">
            App de acompanhamento de hábitos com API REST (FastAPI), dashboard Next.js e autenticação JWT.
          </p>
          <p class="c-project-kpi">✦ −40% custo de leitura em janelas grandes</p>
          <span class="c-project-link">Ver case →</span>
        </div>
      </a>

      <!-- Relatorium -->
      <a class="c-project-card" href="/projects/p5/">
        <img
          class="c-project-img"
          src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1518770660439-4636190af475?auto=format&fm=jpg&w=1200&q=80"
          alt="Relatorium — Quick Activity Button, app Flutter para gestão rural"
          loading="lazy"
        />
        <div class="c-project-body">
          <div class="c-project-meta">
            <span class="c-project-year">2023</span>
            <span class="c-project-tag">Tempo</span>
          </div>
          <h2 class="c-project-name">Relatorium</h2>
          <p class="c-project-desc">
            Componente Flutter para dashboards operacionais rurais — atalhos rápidos acessíveis com navegação consistente.
          </p>
          <p class="c-project-kpi">✦ 45s → 20–25s no registro — −40–55% cliques</p>
          <span class="c-project-link">Ver case →</span>
        </div>
      </a>

    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="c-section-divider"><hr /></div>

  <!-- SOBRE -->
  <section class="c-sobre" id="sobre">
    <div class="c-sobre-left">
      <p class="c-section-label">Sobre</p>
    </div>
    <div class="c-sobre-right">
      <p class="c-sobre-text">
        Trabalho com front-end, back-end e mobile, com prioridade em clareza de arquitetura, acessibilidade e métricas de produto. Já atuei em projetos privados em produção e em iniciativas open-source, sempre buscando reduzir fricção e aumentar previsibilidade de entrega.
      </p>
      <p class="c-sobre-text">
        Se você tem um projeto e quer conversar sobre escopo, riscos e próximos passos — eu retorno com perguntas técnicas e um caminho de execução.
      </p>
      <div class="c-sobre-stack">
        <span class="c-stack-tag">Astro / React</span>
        <span class="c-stack-tag">TypeScript</span>
        <span class="c-stack-tag">NestJS</span>
        <span class="c-stack-tag">Next.js</span>
        <span class="c-stack-tag">Flutter</span>
        <span class="c-stack-tag">PostgreSQL</span>
        <span class="c-stack-tag">Redis</span>
        <span class="c-stack-tag">IndexedDB</span>
        <span class="c-stack-tag">Docker</span>
        <span class="c-stack-tag">Prometheus</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="c-section-divider"><hr /></div>

  <!-- CONTATO -->
  <section class="c-contato" id="contato">
    <div class="c-contato-inner">
      <div>
        <h2 class="c-contato-headline">
          Quer tirar sua ideia<br />do papel com<br /><em>engenharia bem feita?</em>
        </h2>
        <p class="c-contato-sub">
          Me conte contexto, restrições e objetivo.<br />
          Eu retorno com perguntas técnicas e um caminho de execução.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="c-contato-actions">
        <a class="c-contato-btn c-contato-btn--primary" href="https://wa.me/5548984586949" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
          <span class="c-btn-icon">💬</span> WhatsApp
        </a>
        <a class="c-contato-btn" href="mailto:victor.de.alcantara.bueno@gmail.com">
          <span class="c-btn-icon">✉</span> victor.de.alcantara.bueno@gmail.com
        </a>
        <a class="c-contato-btn" href="https://linkedin.com/in/victor-de-alcantara/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
          <span class="c-btn-icon">↗</span> LinkedIn
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  </div>

  <Fragment slot="footer">
    <div class="c-footer-links">
      <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/victor-de-alcantara/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">LinkedIn</a>
      <a href="https://github.com/Salazarismo" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub</a>
      <a href="mailto:victor.de.alcantara.bueno@gmail.com">Email</a>
      <a href="https://wa.me/5548984586949" target="_blank" rel="noopener">WhatsApp</a>
    </div>
    <span class="c-footer-copy">© 2026 Victor de Alcântara Bueno</span>
  </Fragment>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .page-client {
    background: var(--c-charcoal);
    color: var(--c-off-white);
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    min-height: 100dvh;
    overflow-x: hidden;
    position: relative;
  }

  .page-client::before {
    content: '';
    position: fixed;
    inset: 0;
    background-image: url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg viewBox='0 0 256 256' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cfilter id='noise'%3E%3CfeTurbulence type='fractalNoise' baseFrequency='0.9' numOctaves='4' stitchTiles='stitch'/%3E%3C/filter%3E%3Crect width='100%25' height='100%25' filter='url(%23noise)' opacity='0.04'/%3E%3C/svg%3E");
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 0;
    opacity: 0.5;
  }
</style>

<style is:global>
  @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,600;1,300;1,400&family=Syne:wght@400;500;700;800&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@300;400&display=swap');

  :root {
    --c-charcoal:    #1a1a1a;
    --c-charcoal-2:  #222222;
    --c-amber:       #c8922a;
    --c-amber-light: #e0a83a;
    --c-off-white:   #f0ece4;
    --c-muted:       #7a7570;
    --c-border:      rgba(200, 146, 42, 0.18);
    --c-border-dim:  rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
  }

  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

  body { background: var(--c-charcoal); }

  /* NAV */
  nav[aria-label="Principal"] {
    position: fixed;
    top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
    z-index: 100;
    padding: 1.4rem 2.5rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--c-border-dim);
    background: rgba(26,26,26,0.88);
    backdrop-filter: blur(14px);
  }

  .c-nav-logo {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    color: var(--c-off-white);
    text-decoration: none;
    opacity: 0.85;
  }
  .c-nav-logo span { color: var(--c-amber); }

  .c-nav-links {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 2rem;
  }
  .c-nav-links a {
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--c-muted);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }
  .c-nav-links a:hover { color: var(--c-amber); }

  .c-nav-right {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .c-nav-lang {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.6rem;
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.68rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
  }
  .c-nav-lang a {
    color: var(--c-muted);
    text-decoration: none;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }
  .c-nav-lang a:hover,
  .c-nav-lang a.active { color: var(--c-amber); }
  .c-nav-lang span { color: var(--c-border); }

  .c-nav-cta {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--c-amber);
    text-decoration: none;
    border: 1px solid var(--c-border);
    padding: 0.45rem 1rem;
    transition: background 0.2s, color 0.2s;
  }
  .c-nav-cta:hover {
    background: var(--c-amber);
    color: var(--c-charcoal);
  }

  /* HERO */
  .c-hero {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    padding: 14rem 2.5rem 7rem;
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .c-hero::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 40%;
    right: -10%;
    width: 500px;
    height: 500px;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse, rgba(200,146,42,0.05) 0%, transparent 70%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .c-hero-eyebrow {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.68rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.22em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--c-amber);
    margin-bottom: 1.8rem;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: c-fadeUp 0.6s ease forwards 0.1s;
  }

  .c-hero-headline {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: clamp(2.6rem, 6vw, 4.8rem);
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1.08;
    color: var(--c-off-white);
    margin-bottom: 1.6rem;
    max-width: 780px;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: c-fadeUp 0.7s ease forwards 0.2s;
  }
  .c-hero-headline em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--c-amber-light);
  }

  .c-hero-sub {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: clamp(1rem, 1.8vw, 1.2rem);
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: rgba(240,236,228,0.65);
    max-width: 520px;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: c-fadeUp 0.7s ease forwards 0.35s;
  }

  .c-hero-action {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--c-charcoal);
    background: var(--c-amber);
    text-decoration: none;
    padding: 0.85rem 1.8rem;
    transition: background 0.2s, transform 0.2s;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: c-fadeUp 0.7s ease forwards 0.45s;
  }
  .c-hero-action:hover {
    background: var(--c-amber-light);
    transform: translateY(-1px);
  }

  /* DIVIDER */
  .c-section-divider {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 2.5rem;
  }
  .c-section-divider hr {
    border: none;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--c-border-dim);
  }

  /* PROJECTS */
  .c-projects {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 6rem 2.5rem;
  }

  .c-section-label {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.22em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--c-amber);
    margin-bottom: 3.5rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
  }
  .c-section-label::after {
    content: '';
    flex: 1;
    max-width: 60px;
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--c-border);
  }

  .c-projects-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .c-project-card {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    border: 1px solid var(--c-border-dim);
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.02);
    text-decoration: none;
    color: inherit;
    transition: border-color 0.3s, background 0.3s, transform 0.3s;
    overflow: hidden;
    position: relative;
  }
  .c-project-card::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(200,146,42,0.06), transparent 55%);
    opacity: 0;
    transition: opacity 0.3s;
  }
  .c-project-card:hover {
    border-color: rgba(200,146,42,0.4);
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.035);
    transform: translateY(-3px);
  }
  .c-project-card:hover::before { opacity: 1; }

  .c-project-img {
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 16/9;
    object-fit: cover;
    display: block;
    filter: saturate(0.7) brightness(0.75);
    transition: filter 0.4s;
  }
  .c-project-card:hover .c-project-img {
    filter: saturate(0.9) brightness(0.88);
  }

  .c-project-body {
    padding: 1.6rem 1.5rem 1.4rem;
    flex: 1;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .c-project-meta {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
  }

  .c-project-year {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.6rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.16em;
    color: var(--c-muted);
  }

  .c-project-tag {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.6rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.16em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--c-amber);
    border: 1px solid var(--c-border);
    padding: 0.2rem 0.55rem;
  }

  .c-project-name {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.25;
    color: var(--c-off-white);
    margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
  }

  .c-project-desc {
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: var(--c-muted);
    flex: 1;
    margin-bottom: 1.4rem;
  }

  .c-project-kpi {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--c-amber-light);
    margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
  }

  .c-project-link {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    color: rgba(240,236,228,0.4);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    transition: color 0.2s, gap 0.2s;
  }
  .c-project-card:hover .c-project-link {
    color: var(--c-amber);
    gap: 0.9rem;
  }

  /* SOBRE */
  .c-sobre {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 6rem 2.5rem;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 2fr;
    gap: 5rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .c-sobre-text {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: clamp(1.05rem, 1.7vw, 1.22rem);
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1.85;
    color: rgba(240,236,228,0.72);
    margin-bottom: 1.6rem;
  }

  .c-sobre-stack {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  .c-stack-tag {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.62rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    color: var(--c-muted);
    border: 1px solid var(--c-border-dim);
    padding: 0.3rem 0.75rem;
  }

  /* CONTATO */
  .c-contato {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 6rem 2.5rem 10rem;
  }

  .c-contato-inner {
    border: 1px solid var(--c-border-dim);
    padding: 3.5rem 4rem;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.015);
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .c-contato-headline {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 3vw, 2.6rem);
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1.2;
    color: var(--c-off-white);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .c-contato-headline em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--c-amber-light);
  }

  .c-contato-sub {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: rgba(240,236,228,0.55);
  }

  .c-contato-actions {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .c-contato-btn {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    padding: 1rem 1.5rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    border: 1px solid var(--c-border-dim);
    color: var(--c-off-white);
    background: transparent;
    transition: border-color 0.2s, background 0.2s, transform 0.2s;
  }
  .c-contato-btn:hover {
    border-color: rgba(200,146,42,0.4);
    background: rgba(200,146,42,0.06);
    transform: translateX(4px);
  }
  .c-contato-btn--primary {
    border-color: var(--c-amber);
    color: var(--c-charcoal);
    background: var(--c-amber);
  }
  .c-contato-btn--primary:hover {
    background: var(--c-amber-light);
    border-color: var(--c-amber-light);
    transform: translateX(4px);
  }

  .c-btn-icon {
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  /* FOOTER */
  footer[role="contentinfo"] {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    padding: 1.8rem 2.5rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--c-border-dim);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 1rem;
    background: var(--c-charcoal);
  }

  .c-footer-links {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }
  .c-footer-links a {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--c-muted);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }
  .c-footer-links a:hover { color: var(--c-amber); }

  .c-footer-copy {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.62rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: rgba(122,117,112,0.5);
  }

  /* ANIMATIONS */
  @keyframes c-fadeUp {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(18px); }
    to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }

  /* RESPONSIVE */
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .c-projects-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
    .c-sobre { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 2.5rem; }
    .c-contato-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 2.5rem; padding: 2.5rem; }
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    nav[aria-label="Principal"] { padding: 1.2rem 1.5rem; }
